snippet.title: Jak and Daxter: The Lost Levels Gameplay [HQ]
snippet.description:
Gameplay from the original unpublished Jak and Daxter made in the 1990s but was never released. 

You can find the game here http://www.jakanddaxterlegend.com/en/game.html



GBA Music from Harry Potter.
